               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. They promised if I would confess and tell every thing, they would not hurt me, that they suspected somebody else more than me.</p>
               <p>W. R. NASH. I suspected both the porters, and told him if he acknowledged where all the property was, I would do all I could with his master.</p>
